    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your adulation of death not only shields you from your fears, it allows you to feed on them.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Wis 19, Deadhand Style x€ , Improved Unarmed Strike, Knowledge (religion) 6 ranks, ki pool class feature, nongood alignment.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While using Deadhand Style, as long as you have at least 1 point in your ki pool, your bonus on saving throws against fear effects increases to +4, and the DC of Intimidate checks attempted against you increases by 8. <br/><br/> Additionally, if an enemy targets you with a fear effect, you can spend 1 point from your ki pool as an immediate action to gain a number of temporary hit points equal to twice your Hit Dice.",
